{"id": 2643, "genre": 1000, "title": "有了互联网之后你都是怎么记东西的？", "description": "记东西这件事，怎么从“记住内容本身”变成了“记住如何检索”的？（题图来自：iStock ©️ enisaksoy）", "record_count": 18727, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181126200649GtAXmCbEDl1jdsgq.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-26T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5008, "title": "有了互联网之后你都是怎么记东西的？", "content": "有了互联网之后你都是怎么记东西的？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 313204, "content": "不记帐号密码，反正可以用手机号登录/找回", "image": "img/option/option/20181126195727DjKe1RM3votgLU2Y.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 313205, "content": "出去玩的时候，记录旅程的方式主要是拍照", "image": "img/option/option/20181126195706AHperMq6xTuzsgEh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 313206, "content": "不用特意记住跟别人说了啥，翻翻对话记录就行", "image": "img/option/option/20181126195647k2ihuQSavsebj0J6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 313207, "content": "看到有趣的东西，第一反应是“截图”方便以后找", "image": "img/option/option/20181126195612dXlr9ZTQeFoVKPIi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 313208, "content": "任何新闻，只要记住关键词就能随时在网上找到", "image": "img/option/option/20181126195540LnewcZx7zCUDH0f8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 313213, "content": "手机备忘录/微信文件传输助手/收藏夹/…代替纸笔", "image": "img/option/option/20181126195630CkT08VruMeoQRgf2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 313215, "content": "忘记某个字怎么写，直接在手机输入法候选栏里找", "image": "img/option/option/20181126180146BCbvnNDQFajMrqhS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 313222, "content": "记不住地址，连自己前年住哪都要翻淘宝收货地址", "image": "img/option/option/20181126195440tNuZ1daIjkXQf9i4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}